parameters: '最強の敵！その名はシャチ市長！！の巻'

Shark Broccoli: Great Shark Duke... You seem tense. It's the
last of the four major organizations in the city...
"Ultramarvelous Seahunters" are a formidable opponent, so
it's understandable...

Memimi: Great Boss... I am not foolish enough to
overestimate my own strength. The boss's "Dynamite Abalone"
is undoubtedly a formidable enemy, despite the few matches
he's had. I will give it my all... However, I cannot
guarantee a victory...

The opponent Memimi faces, Dynamite Abalone, is considered
the strongest monster in the city. The reason for the few
matches is that opponents run away, preventing Monster
Fights from taking place. The 7 recorded matches all ended
with a one-hit TKO within 3 seconds.

There are also tales of him single-handedly annihilating an
organization that ambushed him, and lifting a light truck to
throw at a detention center to break out his comrades. These
are just rumors, but they are enough to make one believe in
the terrifying aura of this monster...

Memimi: (Still, I will win... I've been simulating it in my
head! If anyone can... No, I'm the only one who can defeat
that monster...!)

Bunny-chan: Hmm... Even so, Mr. Dynamite Abalone is late.
The time for the face-off has long passed... Monster Fights
are supposed to be punctual...
Memimi: Whoa, what's that!? Who is that...?

Shark Broccoli: Dynamite Abalone!! You're a mess... Were you
run over by a dump truck or something?

Dynamite Abalone: Gahh... No... It's not that... Eeeek...
That guy, he's a monster...!! I've never seen such a
creature... My entire organization was taken down by him...

Memimi: Huh...? Dynamite... Abalone has been... defeated...?
Even the strongest monster has...

???: Shashasha... Such small fry is considered the
strongest? Shark Broccoli... The monsters in this city have
really weakened, haven't they?

Shark Broccoli: Hmm... You are...! "Orca Asparagus"!! What
does the current mayor want here...?

Memimi: Sha... Eh, an acquaintance...? The current mayor...?
Great Boss, who is this guy...?

Mayor Orca: Don't call me by my old monster name... Ever
since you gouged out my prized asparagus, I've been going by
"Mayor Orca." I even had my monster suit repaired so I
wouldn't forget that humiliation.

Shark Broccoli: This man is the one who fought me for the
mayor's seat of Doritoku City five years ago... His monster
name was "Orca Asparagus"... Although I inflicted some
injuries on him, I was defeated, and Doritoku City fell into
his hands, ushering in a dark era.

Memimi's eyes widened in shock as she looked at the
intruder. If Shark Broccoli's story was true... then this
monster was not only the nemesis of the organization she
most respected but also responsible for ruining the place
Memimi loved most...

Memimi: You... You're the mayor who took office five years
ago... Because of you... everything in the city went mad...!
You're the one who... destroyed the orphanage where I
lived...!!

Mayor Orca: Oh, so you're from the orphanage, little one. My
bad... All the orphanages in the city were shut down 2 or 3
years ago to make way for pachinko parlors!

Mayor Orca: Well, thanks to that, we've reduced unnecessary
taxes and I got a nice kickback. Everyone must be happy
about it, right? Citizens should contribute to their mayor
after all~?

Memimi: Gaaaaaaaah!!! I will never forgive you...! Shark
Rising!!!

Mayor Orca: What a noisy little brat! I have business with
Shark Broccoli... Go away!

Memimi: Guh!!? Gahh... *cough* How foolish... My full-
powered Shark Rising was stopped with just one hand...

Shark Broccoli: What business do you have with the
underworld of our city now? A man like you who has both
money and status has no need to meddle in our world.

Mayor Orca: Shashasha! Oh, I have no interest in such crappy
monster organizations! My business is strictly with you.

Mayor Orca: Still don't get it? It's "delicious powder,"
"delicious powder"! That stuff is definitely a gold mine!!
I'll mass-produce it in factories and sell it all over the
world to make a fortune!!!

Mayor Orca: If we export it overseas, the retail price will
skyrocket...! How about it, Shark Broccoli... I'll give you
10 million... Hand over the recipe for the delicious powder!

Shark Broccoli: Orca Asparagus... Do you think I would lend
my strength to your money-making schemes? It's futile...

Mayor Orca: Hey hey, Shark Broccoli... Have you forgotten
our mascot wrestling days? If we had enough money back then,
our organization wouldn't have gone under...
Memimi: Shark Jurassic!!! Shark Piranha!!! Shark Ghost!!!

Memimi: *panting* You dare mock the Great Boss, scum!! If
you're a monster too, then earn what you want through our
city's monster rules!! Monster Fight!!!

Memimi: *panting* Ugh... Let's do this... Right now, I am
ready...

Bunny-chan: Mo-Monster Fight!! The management headquarters
accepts! Until the day of the match, contact between
competing monsters is prohibited! Prohibited!! Uh, what's
being wagered is the recipe for delicious powder and... umm,
umm...

Mayor Orca: ...Hmph, well fine... That might be interesting.
Hey, what do you want? Money or status?

Memimi: Everything about you!! If I win, you will resign as
mayor and transfer all your wealth and status to Shark
Broccoli Great Boss!!!

Shark Broccoli: Sh-Shark Great Duke... You're getting too
excited...

Mayor Orca: You're talking nonsense... No matter what, the
recipe for the powder and the position of mayor aren't
equivalent!! Put up something else as your bet.
Memimi: Hmm... What? What do you want!

Mayor Orca: Right now, I'm making a stupid amount of money
with an erotic video streaming service... And lately,
there's been a buzz in town about a beauty who outshines
even idols. Don't you think it would be incredibly
profitable to stream her adult video?
Memimi: What are you talking about... I don't understand...

Mayor Orca: You too, put everything on the line!! If I win,
you'll become an actress at the level of adult videos on the
spot! The video we shoot will be distributed worldwide
through my streaming service...

Memimi: Alright! I'll bet that much without hesitation!!
Wash your neck and wait for the match...
Memimi: Huh? What did you just say...
Shark Broccoli: Sh-Shark Great Duke...? Hey...!

Mayor Orca: Shashasha~! This might make more than the
delicious powder! Wash your pussy and wait... Shasha!

Drillmaid: I've found quite the interesting fool, haven't I,
Brother Shark Broccoli... A complete idiot, just like you...
Drill, drill...
Shark Broccoli: Drillmaid... Have you changed too...

Memimi found herself in a battle where she wagered not only
the recipe for the delicious powder but also her appearance
in an adult video against an extraordinarily strong
monster...

Memimi: ...Before I knew it, the day of the match has
come... Don't be nervous, just defeat the detestable
enemy... Let's head to the venue...
